OL,6,FGas bills are set to go up again
OL,7,Facross the after Islands Energy Group
OL,8,Fannounced it would increase its
OL,9,Fstanding charge.
OL,11,FFrom Tuesday 14 May, all domestic and
OL,12,Fbusiness customers of Guernsey Energy
OL,13,Fand Island Energy will see 10% added
OL,14,Fto the daily cost for accessing the
OL,15,Fmains network.
OL,17,FIt is paid by everyone, regardless of
OL,18,Fhow much gas they use and means the
OL,19,Faverage household will need to shell
OL,20,Fout around #14 extra a year.
